Problem statement:
Implement an application that will perform the following actions:

1.	Prompt the user and read in value for the year of their birth (e.g. 1994)
2.	Prompt the user and read in a value for the month of their birth(e.g. 2 for February)
3.	Prompt the user and read in a value for the day of their birth (e.g. 14).
4.	Print out the day of the week (Sunday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, or Saturday) on which that day falls for year.

	e.g. "You were born on a Sunday"

